               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18410301-name-956" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18410301-name-956" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410301-name-956" type="surname" value="CLARKE"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410301-name-956" type="given" value="SARAH"></interp>SARAH CLARKE</persName>
                  </hi>. I am servant to Thomas Geeves, who keeps the Queen's Head public-house—on the 2nd of March I was up stairs, and saw the prisoner in the bed-room—I asked him what he was doing—he went away—I gave information to my master—I missed the gown now produced, which is my master's.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18410301-name-957" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18410301-name-957" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410301-name-957" type="surname" value="GBEVBS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410301-name-957" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS GBEVBS</persName>
                  </hi>. I keep this public-house. On the 2nd of March I received information from Clarke—I began to see if all was right—the pri<lb></lb>soner had no right in my bed-room—I found my gown was gone—I sent two people in search of the prisoner—I found him in a court in Maiden-lane—he had thrown down the gown and brush in the court—I did not see him do it—it was my wife's gown—not five minutes had elapsed between my finding the gown and the prisoner's going down from the room—it was safe at twelve o'clock, and this was nearly five—no one else had been in the room.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18410301-name-958" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18410301-name-958" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410301-name-958" type="surname" value="MELEY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410301-name-958" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM MELEY</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Off-alley. I was in the public-house, and saw the prisoner coming down stairs with something under his coat—I could not see what it was—I ran and overtook him, and he threw the gown down.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was in a state of intoxication.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
